        "data": "<h1 id=\"01H8066N1X71BMWR8KPQVMTM4A\" class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n<p>The services update for 05/14/2024 is a Major update for <strong>webserver, </strong>minor update for<strong> database,</strong> and patch update for<strong> Backup </strong>service.</p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1X678XQSM8P38E9Q5Z\">DXP Cloud Stack - 05/14/2024 </h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 631px; height: 214px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2891px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 371.609px; height: 62px; background-color: #969996;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.17.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2891px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.17.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 371.609px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/backup:5.17.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">CI</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.5</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2891px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.6</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 371.609px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/jenkins:2.356-jdk8-5.2.6</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Database</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.4.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2891px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.5.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 371.609px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/database:5.5.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">Liferay</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.6.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2891px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.7.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 371.609px; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.7.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.3-5.7.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.7.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.1-5.7.0<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.0-5.7.0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2891px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.3.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 371.609px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:8.12.1-5.3.0 liferaycloud/elasticsearch:7.17.18-5.3.0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 84.8047px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Webserver</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 68.2969px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.4.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 61.2891px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>6.0.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 371.609px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/nginx:1.21.6-6.0.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YWTXV16JYNYMDV6F4\">Change Log</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto; height: 204px; width: 642px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 89.1406px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 73.125px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 92.1406px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket No.</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 342.594px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 89.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 73.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.17.1</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 92.1406px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-36696\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-36696</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 342.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">Fix: Properly handle individual data source failures during backup creation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 89.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 73.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 92.1406px; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-37260\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-37260</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 342.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">Fix: Backup restores must rely on database snapshots first*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 89.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Database</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 73.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.5.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 92.1406px; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-32617\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-32617</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 342.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">Adds <strong>Internal</strong> support to provision postgres projects on test environments*</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 89.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Webserver</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 73.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>6.0.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 92.1406px; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-30691\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-30691*</a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 342.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 44px;\">Security Update: Use Non-privileged user as primary owner</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>Note* :</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-37260\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-37260</a> : Is a regression that was introduced in Backup service version <em><strong>5.16.0</strong></em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-32617\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-32617</a> : Provides capability to provision projects with Postgres database instances for <strong>internal users only. *Not for customers*</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-underline\"><strong>Breaking Change</strong></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-30691\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LCD-30691*</a> : As of web server version 6.0.0+, the <em><strong>nginx.conf</strong></em> file does not allow custom configurations that require root user permissions. See <a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/liferay-cloud/reference/breaking-changes#changes-to-the-web-server-service\">Breaking Changes</a> for more information.</p>\n<p><em>If you are <strong>NOT</strong> using any custom configuration, this change should not impact you in any way. </em></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HFQQE47127T9RVN8YK7MKH4R\">Update Instructions</h2>\n<p><strong>Note</strong><span> : To take advantage of the new features and fixes provided by the 5.x stack of services, you must update your entire stack to the new 5.x images.</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YDXGGCTPJ2C2XKQWE\">Image Update Instructions</h2>\n<p>The Liferay Cloud image versions needs to be set inside of the &lt;service&gt;/LCP.json file.</p>\n<p>Note, however, that the liferay service uses two image properties. The DXP Cloud image is set in the liferay/LCP.json file, but the liferay/dxp image is set in the gradle.properties. This change was made in order to facilitate easier deployment using the Liferay Cloud CLI.</p>\n<p>liferay/LCP.json file would set the liferaycloud/liferay-dxp image:</p>\n<pre><span>\"image\"</span>:<span>\"liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.0.X\"</span></pre>\n<p>liferay/gradle.properties file would set the liferay/dxp image:</p>\n<pre><span>liferay.workspace.docker.image.liferay</span>=<span>liferay/dxp:7.4-x</span><span></span></pre>\n<p>For all other images, you will just need to update the LCP.json file with the intended image version.</p>\n<p>Once the LCP.json files are updated, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n<pre>git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"Update dxp cloud stack to XXX\"</pre>\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>"
      },
